➜河南诗人卧龙：独处
http://www.sohu.com/a/423727743_100115135	45789
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201010/25514280125e40f986f23155b8371dec.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>独处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/卧龙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霜花日将老，冬夜近濒临。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁料云无性，偏逢冷雨阴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201010/7f99a06f5ccc43b28bf65b8fbb466490.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>高云伟，笔名：卧龙，1962年出生，河南南阳油田工作。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201010/c639b07385524c94b03d975a76843f23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
